data.description: Looking for a spacious home on acreage? Look no further than this stunning property that offers 4606 SF w/ 6 bdrms & 4.5 bthrms on a rare 6-acre lot! Large Kitchen w/ island & ss appliances, vaulted LR, Primary Bdrm & 2 other large bdrms on the main level. The lower level features a large Rec Rm w/ wet bar & 3 additional bdrms, perfect for bdrms, guests, hobbies or home office. Newer Roof. Barn. Enjoy the outdoors with plenty of room for gardening or your own hobby farm. This is country living at its best!
